author: Justin Hoyo
text:
Not my resident gym, but decided to give it a try! The equipment here are well-maintained. Power racks are sufficient with competition-standard barbells. However the free-weights area needs some improvements. Benches and dumbbells are not maintained properly.

I would say this is more of a powerlifting gym (discouraged for regular gym-goers). The lifters here often ‚Äúhog‚Äù the racks, come in big groups, and take LONG rest times. Properly wouldn‚Äôt visit this gym again.

Staff here are friendly though! :)

author: Syahiran
text:
Very well-organised gym with a clean and welcoming environment. The staff, particularly Ana, went above and beyond to help me with my needs and queries. She is really friendly and euphoric throughout our interaction.

This isn‚Äôt my home club but would gladly recommend to anyone who is a member or who is looking to sign up. 10/10.

author: Jack
text:
This is not my home club as it's not near where I stay or work, but having visited it for the first time last week I wished this was my home gym!
The layout is great, so many different machines that I do not see in other AF, especially back machines. There's a nice view from the 2nd floor. And best part is, lots of sports outlet stores here to get your latest workout gear!

author: Will
text:
The staff at the counter is friendly and the place is so well laid out and personalised. The ladies has many items for sharing.

But there is only 1 toilet. Makes waiting for it difficult.

author: E Lee
text:
Best AF so far IN THE EAST! except the choice of music during midnight.. the hardstyle music has to go!!
Nice new equipments, tons of it, a good range, gym is clean and well maintained. Lots of foam rollers, very thoughtful. Gym has good ventilation, lots of fans and the aircon is good! Personally love the toilets as it‚Äôs separated between male and female.

author: Judy Tan
text:
My home gym. I‚Äôd go around to try out the other AF gyms with high ratings since I signed up end of last year. Feels like the ratings of some of them are solicited but oh well.

This one is deserving though. Everyone in there are like friends and really welcoming. I bumped into Amirah near my home couple of weeks after I signed up and she called out to me by name. Like how did she even remember my name even if she remembered my face after such a short period of time?

The gym is clean, users are mostly friendly and willing to rotate/share equipments. Love that the gym equipments are well maintained.

Male and female bathrooms are separated (rare for Anytime Fitness gyms).

I‚Äôm so relieved this is my home gym. Phew.

author: Avinash Gopal
text:
This gym is top-notch with all the latest equipment and amazing personal trainers.
I‚Äôm so glad I have it as my home gym!

PT Bumi‚Äôs training sessions are incredible and really help me stay focused on my fitness goals.

author: Razin
text: Really big, spacious and lots of equipment here to play with. The staff are really friendly, helpful and proactive,  namely Nur Amirah. Can get really crowded during peak hours, which is normal, but is well compensated with the varieties of equipments available.

author: Muhammad Yusri Ng Yang Yun
text: Great gym overall! The equipment is top-notch, and the vibes/ambiance are really nice. The staff is super friendly, and the service is a solid 10/10. I also appreciated that when I wanted to cancel, they didn‚Äôt pressure me to stay, which says a lot about their professionalism. The changing rooms are always tidy and clean. The only minor downside is that they sometimes reply late, but everything else is great.  üòä

author: Philip Koh
text: Spacious layout. Comfortable environment. Fantastic staff and personal trainers. The staff are knowledgeable, helpful and friendly and add immense value to my fitness experience. There are numerous equipment and they are new! Definitely have an enjoyable time every time I visit.

author: Isnarti Noordin
text:
Love the ambience at this gym. It‚Äôs a safe space and welcoming place  for gym goers , with top notch equipment and wonderful staff.

It‚Äôs a pretty spacious gym with quite a big variety of machines that you don‚Äôt usually find in other AF gyms.   Place is generally neat and equipment are well maintained. Nice to see that they provide each equipment with sanitizer spray and wipe down towel.

The higher ceiling and natural light from the many surrounding windows add on to the feeling of spaciousness and good energy at this gym.

Very friendly and welcoming staff at the gym too!

The only unfortunate recent development happening ,  the mall is under renovation and reconfiguration, leading to a relocation of nearest escalator further away as well as shrinkage of free space / stretching area.

author: Muzammil Peer
text:
I've been a member of Anytime Fitness CCP for a while now, and it has truly been a fantastic experience. The gym boasts a vast space with well-thought-out equipment placement, ensuring plenty of room to work out comfortably. The ambience is great, making it a conducive environment for all gym-goers.

The amenities are top-notch, and the toilets are always fully stocked. However, it would be even better if there were at least one more toilet facility in the gents. ü§£

I must highlight the exceptional service provided by Shah, the most brilliant staff member at Anytime Fitness CCP. Shah is incredibly helpful and makes everyone feel right at home. He takes immense pride in his work, ensuring that no issue goes unnoticed. His dedication to providing the best experience for gym-goers is truly commendable. Shah's attention to detail and willingness to go above and beyond make him a standout asset to the gym.

Overall, Anytime Fitness CCP offers a wonderful gym experience, and Shah's outstanding service is the cherry on top. Highly recommended!

author: William Charles
text:
I would like to express my heartfelt appreciation for the exceptional team at this gym outlet (CCP) Bumi, Shah, Ari, Amirah, Allyssya, and Ana are amazing. Each of them has consistently demonstrated professionalism, dedication, and a genuine passion for creating an excellent fitness experience.

Bumi brings an unparalleled level of energy and positivity that motivates both staff and members. Shah's commitment to ensuring a smooth operation is evident in his reliability and attention to detail. Ari's knowledge and willingness to go above and beyond have been key to our success. Amirah‚Äôs warmth and attentiveness make everyone feel welcome, while Allyssya‚Äôs organizational skills and cheerful demeanor have been invaluable. Lastly, Ana‚Äôs proactive approach and infectious enthusiasm have left a lasting impression.

Keep up the incredible work!

author: Hejaz Goush
text: Amirah and Ari at the Changi City Point branch of Anytime Fitness are absolutely fantastic! They are incredibly friendly, helpful, and always go above and beyond to make members feel welcome. Their positive energy has created such a warm and inviting atmosphere in the gym, making every visit a pleasure. Whether you're a seasoned gym-goer or a newcomer, they‚Äôre always ready to assist. Highly recommend this gym, thanks to the amazing team!

author: Spartan Dan
text:
First time coming here since I knew last time this place was gonna open up.

When I enter the gym and I saw 4 power racks, I know this gym is gonna be good.

Toilets were clean. And toiletries provided was useful. Appreciate it. Donwside is that only have one toilet so there is once, I need to go use and someone was using so I had to hold my pee in for a bit üòÇ

Other than that, can see people were nice too. Environment is fresh and clean. Spacious. Maybe cause I went in a non peak hrs. But can imagine if it's crowded. But with such huge space, I think can accommodate la.

Equipment were in good condition. Barbells, power racks, deadlift platforms. Dumbbells, barbells and ez curl bars. Not forgetting the machines. All is good. Thanks!! Would definitely visit here again.

author: amdeefitness
text: This is our home base gym. Convenient, clean, and the manager Shah is always upbeat, friendly, and watches out for his clients/gym users. As much as we love the accessibility of the gym and the friendliness of the gym goers there, we would love it if there was a better system for putting back the weights and for sorting them according to weight (difficult I know but we can hope)!!

author: Farah Irfahyanna
text:
I‚Äôve been a member of AF CCP for quite sometime now and I just wanted to leave a review. As I was looking through other gyms‚Äô reviews (because I‚Äôd like to see which is more convenient to my next stop for work) and all I see is bad reviews of the gyms such as low maintenance, bad hygiene, etc.

The gym here is amazing. Great use of space. A lot of machines. Not to mention there‚Äôs separate toilets for males and females (this is really awesome for a hijabi like me!) Staff are friendly and consistent. I‚Äôm not familiar with their names but I can recognise their faces üòô

Location is good with a view too. A lot of outlet stores. Food varieties as well. Highly recommend to come and visit the gym!

Cleanliness: 8.5/10
Machines: 9/10
Staff: 9/10

author: Ian Tan Wee
text:
This review is especially dedicated to one of the staff at Changi City Point AF, Jun Long. Respectable and Professional young individual, from being able to welcome members of this wonderful gym or more so I should say a family. One being such that he is able to make me feel like home in this gym. Another special quality of him, would be being able to guide me through a workout. Able to demonstrate certain movements in various exercises with precision, checking my form and range of motion for me to execute the movement correctly. With such quality of teaching, I am able to stray away from any sort of unnecessary injuries due to bad form.

Thank you Tan Jun Long, you have really make a deep impact on my life. I would highly recommend him to anybody in the gym, who needs a trainer !

author: Donovan Choo
text: Changi City Point is hands down one of the top gyms in Singapore with the environment and the people. One of the more commendable staff is Jay, he is a very friendly Physical Trainer at the gym that is always helping others and welcoming us to the gym. He also has a large clientele of clients which also adds to his repertoire of skills and training principals. Someone I look forward to seeing in the gym constantly.

author: Mohammed Maqsood Ali
text:
I am very happy with this branch; it‚Äôs near my office. The GYM is very clean, everything is working, and the staff are very polite and professional. It's a welcoming, inclusive atmosphere. I would definitely recommend this gym to anyone nervous about starting, but also those with more experience.
Thanks to Lucas, who escorted me to the gym and admissions.

author: Charmailt Ng
text:
Was curious about how the AF is here at Changi City Point so I came to take a peek.

The staff there (Amirah) was very friendly and helped show me the facilities inside the gym.

The gym is spacious, clean and cozy! Im an AF member but I‚Äôm not from AF Changi City Point but I think I want to try gymming here next time hehe :)

author: Shashi Vishwakarma
text:
Very nice and clean gym. Well equipped and not very much crowded.

PT Bumi is well experienced, professional and friendly trainer. Highly recommended.

author: xavier
text: best gym in the east side if ur looking for good and positive vibes. Staff are the best J shawn n kenneth v friendly n funny üí™  just sign up here or come here to gym if u already have a membership üòç‚ù§Ô∏è‚ù§Ô∏èüôè ‚Ä¶

author: Mohammad Noorham Noordin
text: Changi City Point Anytime Fitness is an amazing workout place with a friendly and welcoming atmosphere. The staff and trainers are incredibly knowledgeable and passionate, making every visit enjoyable. The gym is well-equipped and clean, providing a comfortable environment for workouts. The sense of community among the members adds to the positive experience. If you're looking for a gym with great personalities and friendly staff, Changi City Point Anytime Fitness is the perfect choice.

author: Nobu
text:
Gym floor is clean and spacious.
Toilet is always kept clean too.
Love the variety of equipments available in the gym! Nowadays, not many gym have the space and equipment to cover most exercises.

What I don‚Äôt appreciate.
It‚Äôs when specific group of members who have no respect for the gym:
- Wear slippers or crocs while training.
- Tripods everywhere. Sometimes is strange locations. (Tripping hazard)
- Bags on the floor, not at the pigeon holes. (Tripping hazard)
- Liquid/powder chalk bottles on the floor (Again tripping hazards)
- Unnecessary slamming on the platform with no effort to control. I came across many powerlifters and this one of the worst (not even advance level).

If members can‚Äôt respect the gym, it shows how much they respect the gym management.
Perhaps you may wish to look into the standards.

author: Gab ‚Äúgift_of_the_gab‚Äù
text: I‚Äôve been a regular at CCP AF and one thing that I really appreciate at the gym is the very welcoming staff, specifically Jay. Jay was very welcoming whenever I was in the gym. As I was usually in the gym by myself, he would often come up to talk to me which made me feel a lot more comfortable and even encouraged me to push myself further in my workouts (I even set a few PRs because of his encouragement). He is always willing to help my friends and I with exercises that he had learnt and also shows concern when we haven‚Äôt been to the gym in a while. This is one of the reasons I choose to stick with this AF even though it isn‚Äôt the closest outlet to where I live.

author: that guy
text: This review will be dedicated to Shah. During an incident of me misplacing my wallet I immediately seek assistance from the staff on duty, Shah immediately did everything he could to help me. Apart from this incident, he has always been very approachable and sociable with members and prospects. A true passionate staff who serves with passion and diligence.

author: Joel Tan
text:
AF changi city point is the best gym. 10/10

In the gym, J's enthusiasm and energy are contagious. In addition to making the gym feel so friendly, J can also be a great motivator at times. Kenneth and Shawn are the other staff members. Their shared commitment to assisting clients in reaching their fitness objectives as personal trainers are admirable. Additionally, they have a remarkable capacity to challenge clients while keeping them safe. Their dedication to help others in changing their bodies and lives are truly commendable.

Lastly, part of why this gym runs efficiently is thanks to Lucas's great leadership and management abilities, which also foster a positive work atmosphere for both employees and customers. Lucas is a true asset to this fitness community.

author: WanderWithWit
text: One of the most spacious gym located in the east about 7mins from Changi Airport. It is one of the most well equipped anytime fitness gym. The gym is also verrrrry well kept and maintained and I witnessed the instructors themselves cleaning and stacking back the weights when they were not returned properly. Love this gym and will certainly return for my workout. Thank you.

author: Robert Boo
text: Great atmosphere! Enjoyed all the gym sessions here. Friendly staff. Special shout-out to Shawn for being extremely helpful when I needed help with the wifi. Do visit if you wish to gym with the friendliest bunch.

author: Roman LFC Muzz Reigns LFC 4 Ever
